<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/images/logo.png">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@700&family=Open+Sans:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div id="loader-wrapper">
        <div class="loader-content">
            <div id="loading-text-animation"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="main-content">
        <header class="hero">
            <div class="background-blur"></div>
            <div class="container">
                <h1 class="hero-title fade-in-scroll">Welcome to <span>Skypixel</span></h1>
                <p class="hero-subtitle fade-in-scroll" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">Explore our projects and discover creativity!</p>
                <div class="hero-buttons fade-in-scroll" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
                    <a href="#projects" class="btn"><i class="fas fa-briefcase"></i> View Projects</a>
                    <a href="#about" class="btn"><i class="fas fa-users"></i> About Us</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </header>

        <section id="about" class="about section-padding fade-in-scroll">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>About Skypixel</h2>
                <p>Skypixel was formed by a passionate team of developers and creators who share a common goal: to build innovative and impactful projects.</p>
                <h3>Meet the Team</h3>
                <div class="team-grid">
                    <div class="team-card fade-in-scroll">
                        <img src="/images/team1.jpg" alt="Team Member 1 - MaxUltimat3">
                        <h4>MaxUltimat3</h4>
                        <p class="team-role">Lead Developer</p>
                        <p>Max is a full-stack developer passionate about crafting scalable and efficient applications, ensuring robust functionality and optimal performance across all our projects.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="team-card fade-in-scroll" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
                        <img src="/images/team2.jpg" alt="Team Member 2 - Shinigvmi">
                        <h4>Shinigvmi</h4>
                        <p class="team-role">UI/UX Designer</p>
                        <p>Andy specializes in designing user-friendly and intuitive interfaces, enhancing user experience and ensuring seamless interactions with our applications.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="projects" class="projects section-padding fade-in-scroll">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Our Projects</h2>
                <div class="project-grid">
                    <div class="project-card fade-in-scroll">
                        <img src="/images/project1.jpg" alt="Project 1 - Puro" loading="lazy">
                        <div class="project-card-content">
                            <div>
                                <h3>Puro</h3>
                                <p>Puro is a versatile Discord bot designed to enhance member interaction and provide robust moderation tools to secure your Discord server effectively.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="project-buttons">
                                <a href="#" class="btn" data-project="1"><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Details</a>
                                <a href="https://github.com/norbertbaricz/Puro/releases" target="_blank" class="btn btn-secondary"><i class="fas fa-download"></i> Download</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="project-card fade-in-scroll" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
                        <img src="/images/project2.jpg" alt="Project 2 - DakotaAC" loading="lazy">
                        <div class="project-card-content">
                            <div>
                                <h3>DakotaAC</h3>
                                <p>DakotaAC is a powerful Minecraft anti-cheat system, meticulously crafted to protect your Minecraft server from hackers, ensuring a fair and secure gaming environment.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="project-buttons">
                                <a href="#" class="btn" data-project="2"><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Details</a>
                                <a href="https://github.com/norbertbaricz/DakotaAC/releases" target="_blank" class="btn btn-secondary"><i class="fas fa-download"></i> Download</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="project-card fade-in-scroll" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
                        <img src="/images/project3.jpg" alt="Project 3 - Server Launcher" loading="lazy">
                        <div class="project-card-content">
                            <div>
                                <h3>Server Launcher</h3>
                                <p>The Server Launcher is a user-friendly Windows application designed to simplify the management of your home-hosted Minecraft server, making server administration straightforward and efficient.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="project-buttons">
                                <a href="#" class="btn" data-project="3"><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Details</a>
                                <a href="https://github.com/norbertbaricz/Server-Launcher/releases" target="_blank" class="btn btn-secondary"><i class="fas fa-download"></i> Download</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                     <div class="project-card fade-in-scroll" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
                        <img src="/images/project4.jpg" alt="Upcoming Project 1" loading="lazy">
                         <div class="project-card-content">
                            <div>
                                <h3>Skypixel Website</h3>
                                <p>Welcome to the Skypixel website! Here, you can explore all our exciting projects and get to know the talented team behind the innovations. Dive in and discover what Skypixel has to offer!</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="project-buttons">
                                <a href="#" class="btn" data-project="4"><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Details</a>
                                <a href="https://github.com/norbertbaricz/Skypixel/releases" target="_blank" class="btn btn-secondary"><i class="fas fa-download"></i> Download</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="project-card fade-in-scroll" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
                        <img src="/images/project5.jpg" alt="Upcoming Project 2" loading="lazy">
                        <div class="project-card-content">
                            <div>
                                <h3>DX</h3>
                                <p>Get ready for DX, a project that is set to redefine speed, future and safety in its sector. While details are still emerging, expect something truly innovative and powerful!</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="project-buttons">
                                <a href="#" class="btn" data-project="5"><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Details</a>
                                <a href="#" class="btn btn-secondary disabled"><i class="fas fa-download"></i> Download</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <div id="project-popup" class="popup">
            <div class="popup-content">
                <span class="close-btn">&times;</span>
                <h2 id="popup-project-title">Project Details</h2>
                <p id="project-description">Default project description text if not overridden by JS.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <footer class="fade-in-scroll">
            <p>&copy; 2025 Skypixel. All rights reserved.</p>
        </footer>
    </div><script src="/js/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>